    <h2>Part I — The Republic Builds</h2>
    <p>Ten essays tracing the school-trust compact from the 1785 Land Ordinance through admission-era doublings, the school clause, fiduciary breach, the captured-Attorney-General enforcement architecture, and the constituency that remedies it.</p>
