    <p>This booklet is the substrate for the rest of the library. The <a href="/atlas/">Atlas</a>, the <a href="/counting/">Counting House</a>, and the <a href="/reading/sacred-compact-prologue/">Sacred Compact</a> white paper all draw from these state entries.</p>
